_sText:
A skill map where each team uses knifes and there are nades scattered across the map and you try to eliminate the other team, but each team has a medic that can heal his teamates with green gas so first you want to try to assasinate the other teams medic. Makes for interesting gameplay.


Set for up to 32 spawns
